12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 59 O.S. 2021, Section 6001, as
14 last amended by Section 1, Chapter 89, O.S.L. 2023 (59 O.S. Supp.
15 2024, Section 6001), is amended to read as follows:
16 Section 6001. A. 1. There is hereby re-created the State
17 Board of Behavioral Health Licensure to continue until July 1, 2025
18 July 1, 2028, in accordance with the provisions of the Oklahoma
19 Sunset Law.
20 2. Members of the Board shall serve at the pleasure of and may
21 be removed from office by the appointing authority. Members shall
22 continue to serve until their successors are appointed. Any vacancy
23 shall be filled in the same manner as the original appointments.
24 Four members shall constitute a quorum.
